{"tid":1910902,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"ONEPIECE 海賊王 ワンピース973  漫畫 光月一族  中文情報同圖","createTime":"2020-03-05T03:50:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T17:54:15.000Z","uid":3020,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1c5090436b38db783e78eb4b214f98444770dc7b","tid":1910902,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:50:42.000Z","msg":"973話標題 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/REAbhMn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FREAbhMn.jpg&h=b88b5f6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jfgefx3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjfgefx3.jpg&h=44cb1a70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iDSAKro.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiDSAKro.jpg&h=e7e6d44c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n光月一族<br />\n時夫人將桃子跟武士們送往未來後，殞命。<br />\n大蛇找不到武士們死亡的證據，驚懼不已。<br />\n傳次郎為了隱藏真面目，改變了的外表，自稱狂死郎，發展手下。<br />\n扼殺自己的內心跟在大蛇身邊，成為了取代豹五郎的江湖俠客。<br />\n另一方面，作為醜三小子一直竊取金庫的錢財<br />\n之後，發現了與河松走散混入都城的日和，道出了自己的真面目<br />\n懇求她在決戰開始前不要告訴夥伴們自己的真面目<br />\n為了替河松保護她，讓她化名為小紫過活。"},{"pid":"2cde2b1ac49afd7fe1acfbf1f9af10160ff5353e","tid":1910902,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:51:45.000Z","msg":"狂死郎係好 ？唔似喔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a09961e340892dd909ae91cfd422fdf8b796ae37","tid":1910902,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:53:30.000Z","msg":"點解狂死朗同山治打？<br />\n<br />\n又話係好人？唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16013c4321270142786687afc3303754295488a3","tid":1910902,"uid":60164,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:54:36.000Z","msg":"5毛 遠阪凜#3020 手持至少6個連登帳號,請admin跟進<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1291657\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1291657</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n熱烈恭賀牙井當選區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.